message: Hello Bob, I'm excited to offer you our premium product for $100. We believe it's a fair price considering its value and quality.
Thank you for the offer, Alice. I appreciate the value of your product. I would like to propose a counteroffer of $85.
Thank you for your counteroffer, Bob. I understand your valuation of the product. Let me make a proposal of $90 for the product.
I appreciate your willingness to negotiate, Alice. Considering my budget, I would like to propose a counteroffer of $87 for the product.
Thank you for your latest proposal, Bob. After careful consideration, I am willing to accept $92 for the product.
